==================
Firebase Messaging
==================

.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/firebase-messaging.svg
    :alt: PyPI Version
    :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/firebase-messaging

.. image:: https://github.com/sdb9696/firebase-messaging/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg?branch=main
